00:28:42,444 --> 00:28:43,285
of that world guide.

567
00:28:43,905 --> 00:28:47,025
Because the world guide is our fourth, final,

568
00:28:47,265 --> 00:28:48,726
and most important milestone.

569
00:28:49,546 --> 00:28:52,928
When the world guide's done, the product, the cards,

570
00:28:53,308 --> 00:28:57,250
our artist pool is either set up for success or it's not.

571
00:28:59,251 --> 00:29:02,233
So that's the process that we've iterated on

572
00:29:02,553 --> 00:29:05,395
from Lorwyn through Khans of Tarkir.

